Privacy Policy for Echo Flight
Introduction
Welcome to Echo Flight! We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring a safe gaming experience. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our game.

By downloading and using Echo Flight, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with the terms of this policy, please do not use the game.

Information We Collect
1. Information You Provide to Us:

Account Information: If you create an account or profile within the game, we may collect your username and email address.
Customer Support: If you contact us for support, we may collect your name, email address, and any information you provide in your message.
2. Information Collected Automatically:

Device Information: We may collect information about your device, such as the device model, operating system, and unique device identifiers.
Usage Data: We may collect information about how you interact with the game, including the levels you play, your progress, and other gameplay activities.
Log Information: When you use the game, we automatically receive and record certain details from your device, such as your IP address, crash reports, and system activity.
3. Information from Third-Party Services:

If you choose to connect your game account to third-party services (like Google Play Games or social media), we may collect information from these services in accordance with their privacy policies.
How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect to:

Provide, operate, and improve the game;
Personalize your gaming experience;
Respond to your comments and questions and provide customer support;
Monitor and analyze usage and trends to improve your experience;
Protect the security and integrity of the game;
Comply with legal obligations and enforce our terms.
Sharing Your Information
We may share your information with:

Service Providers: We may share your information with third-party service providers who assist us in operating the game and performing services such as hosting, data analysis, and customer support.
Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities (e.g., a court or government agency).
Business Transfers: In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of all or a portion of our assets, your information may be transferred as part of that transaction.
Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no security measures are completely infallible, and we cannot guarantee the security of your information.

Your Rights and Choices
Depending on your location, you may have the following rights regarding your information:

Access and Update: You can access and update your information by contacting us.
Deletion: You can request that we delete your information, subject to certain exceptions.
Objection: You can object to certain processing of your information.
Restriction: You can request that we restrict the processing of your information.
Data Portability: You can request a copy of your information in a structured, machine-readable format.
To exercise these rights, please contact us at the details provided below.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our practices, please contact us at:

Email: coolcatgames01@gmail.com

Thank you for playing Echo Flight!
